name: Till the end (ruanpalmeira)
description:
Made for the Wowie Jam 3.0 of 2021

Help the ball get to the end of the levels.

There's also an Windows version for download.

I really liked the idea and want to expand a bit more, I didn't have much time because of work, but I'll give it some more polish, levels, traps, and some extra ideas after the 1 week of ratings.
